			section.about-us
				.container
					h2 About us
					p We are Soteria Radar. A Pittsburgh-based startup working out of Carnegie Mellon University's Swartz Center for Entrepreneurship to develop hardware which interacts with Connected Vehicles, providing informational inputs and enhancing system effectiveness. We are creating the next generation of intelligent infrastructure and safety devices to ensure stakeholders from cyclists to passengers are out of harm's way.
