							h3 Clayton Edwards
							p A 2019 graduate of Carnegie Mellon University's Master of Public Policy and Management program with an obsession for autonomous vehicles and barriers to their implementation. Through his independent studies and coursework concentrated in entrepreneurship and strategy development this project to aid the adoption of new trends in mobility and smart cities began.
