							h3 Jenny Han
							p Jenny is currently a student in Carnegie Mellon University's, School of Electrical and Computer Engineering with a minor in Human Computer Interaction. Last summer, Jenny worked in the Reliable Autonomous Systems Lab on a social robot which interacts with participants. This robot is located at the 3rd floor of the computer science building at CMU. At Soteria Radar, Jenny's focus is on software development.
					.profile
